Bio

Hi there

Im Rubi, your friendly bio explorer

Reach me at: rubimarch201@gmail.com

Im passionate about liver disease and cancer, especially how the metabolic environment affects disease progression.

Im interested in spatial transcriptomics and multi-omics data integration.

I love exploring how genetic population-specific variation impacts disease risk, particularly in underrepresented populations.

Im always eager to learn new computational and experimental approaches to connect with disease biology.

Hobbies & Interests

  • Playing guitar
  • Reading
  • Learning about music (especially rock)
  • Running
  • Spending time outside
  • Sleeping
  • Watching movies
